Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥真的回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的老师不是和你联络过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使她故意说谎也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喂 内田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 佑那家伙也在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什么关系 总之遥也回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐看起来回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是内田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是今天的例会怎么也要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那要现在回东京吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.05,0:02:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N暴 \N风 \N雨 \N的 \N夜 \N晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是美有树被告白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 不对不对 是明日香啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明日香被田中君告白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好像有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可爱的小客人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…佑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点心的话 在平常摆的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑一直受你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我们才是 总是添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 下次再来我家玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要勇一来 家里就非常热闹 阿姨最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有树 快点过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那过会见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 没有啤酒吗 啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 阿姨怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些醉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也不错啊 很高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 遥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被卷入什么奇怪的事件里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么事啦 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很让人担心啊 到底跑那里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又那样把真相隐瞒起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 后藤刚才在隔壁的房间里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 没…没啦 我一直在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的时候 好像看见二楼的窗户里好像有什么人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是后藤君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心理作用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二楼除了这间屋子以外 全是空房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是都做了储藏室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个是…幽灵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午开始说什么幽灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西有被随便动过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见什么奇怪的声音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你把幽灵赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在身边带着这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可能带着这种东西的吧 普通来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵 退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵 退散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我吧 快成佛吧 请快成佛吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这样可糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏了什么吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什么但是了 快说出来吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们肯定不相信我的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 好友的话 无论说什么肯定都会相信的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 果然是幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事怎么可能让人相信！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界里有未来人 这种话能让人相信么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.13,0:05:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比幽灵的话更不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来来的人什么的 是幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不感让人相信 让那种家伙到家里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我来拆穿那个怪物的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊这家伙 明明是夏天还穿着黑色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙怎么可能是未来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是黑色披风的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥会被骗我可不会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点说出真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来遥这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是从未来来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说说15年后会变成怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 快点说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事要怎么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成干扰过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 不破坏时间的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对我保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口风紧的我肯定会帮你保密的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手啦 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚…惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 不要闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了 我输了啦 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君你准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在和大家一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小孩子们随便玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啊 美有树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 下一次你可要来我家玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安定了呢 已经习惯这个时空了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 我们还能在这个时空存在多久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 现在感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是想着之后的事 也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明摆着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去消灭龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那家伙的力量太强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被送到时空的夹缝中 赢不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住一直在那家伙身边的那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们在这里说再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤不要在藤原家待太久了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去借本书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 我们实在好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 是未来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏着一个穿着怪异服装的不知所谓的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能相信那种事 我们真不是普通人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨不像之前那样啰嗦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那考试不考了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.89,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像燕雀说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是…鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有趣的见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和那家伙的过去面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗 小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有事要找那边的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁和你这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是让我火大的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把你那双眼睛挖出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 你这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的 如果再干涉这个时空的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然时空有不可逆性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但会有什么影响是无法预测…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再妨碍我的话 杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说是从小的玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你给我消失吧 枭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 逃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子们 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个无聊的大叔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要分两路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枭的任务是为确保龙之转矩的位置进而先攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦确保了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人再一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:13:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦肯定会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦的对手由枭来做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要把龙之转矩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验用装置中出现的异常电磁波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被预测为是由量子共鸣现象产生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经传送给了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时在当地勘测到的资料制成的量子现象的图解也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这件事看来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,260)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真无聊~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以推测出在那个区域可能会出现特异的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(448,265)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真无聊~\N\N官僚果然都没有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,340)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真无聊~\N\N官僚果然都没有什么用啊\N \N\N\N\N\N即使说是精英也都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(468,380)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-10}{\bord0\shad1}真无聊~\N\N官僚果然都没有什么用啊\N \N\N\N\N\N即使说是精英也都是笨蛋\N \N这里也都是笨蛋的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是个实验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我认为把实验用的地域扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行对波动的位置能进行综合判断的调查体式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,250)}{\frx-0\fry-8\frz-8}{\bord0\shad1}特别是精英里的女人特别啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是唯一能避免被害的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“被害”这个词我觉得用的不怎么适当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田博士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为绝对临界组织计划委员会的责任…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员长 我有话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府会真的认真考虑量子反应的实用性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的情况下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量资料的暂态通信技术的开发 现在整个世界都在做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对的可是世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们却还在等实验不一定发生的周边地区的影响预测报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不认为效率很糟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 篠原君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险在任何地方都可能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才选在离东京很远的地方做了实验地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是半官半民的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要在奇怪的地方摆出官僚作风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是考虑到了地域的安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要厚颜无耻了 你这个无用的学者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事前调查什么的 我来做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里也培养了很多量子物理学什么的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦的小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为低气压的影响 雄岛会有大雨 出门请当心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雷声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要打到我们家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀盯上了龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果消灭了龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么由于龙之转矩的不可干涉性 会有发动强大能量的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅会导致这个时空的不安定 整个时空都可能会被消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君有打电话过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是约会的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 要小心啊 黑披风的那些家伙又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑披风？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中缆车上袭击我们的家伙 还有另一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 没想到你会先出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩待会解决也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从你开始消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有能力阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 鸦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧 时间停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红秧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去搜查 小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空有难以预测的干涉 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捕获龙之转矩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之转矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是未来的勇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 这是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真火大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完 还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是勇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把遥交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 遥?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护遥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到这个身体消失为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以的啊 那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是勇不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切之所以开始都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.38,0:24:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田你真的相信有另外一个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.94,0:24:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使分开了也依然是朋友啊 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.49,0:25:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 擦身而过
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.71,0:25:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我力所能及的事吗


